verbose_text: This heterogeneous distribution is attributed to the lower amount of Na present in these specific crystals / agglomerates, leading to a higher number of Bronsted acid sites (hence intensely fluorescent crystals).44 In Figure XREF_FIG, the 3 D top-view volumes of : Z80-Al, Z80-Si; Z50-Al, Z50-Si, Z20-Al, and Z20-Si extrudates are presented.
